source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_00<tab>Fyuu wishes you to raid the raiders.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_00<tab>Fyuu aimerait que vous pilliez les pillards.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_01<tab>Word has reached Fyuu that another trading vessel has fallen prey to the Coral Tridents. Though the crew managed to flee unscathed using a landing skiff, their valuable cargo yet remains on the captured ship. Novv's spawnling asks that you attempt to liberate this cargo from the claws of his zealous kin. Borrow an elbst from Pahh, and locate the crates on the deck of the merchantman.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_01<tab>Les Tridents du corail ont volé un bateau marchand rempli de mar<var 16 /var>chan<var 16 /var>di<var 16 /var>ses. L'équipage a pu s'échapper mais toute la cargaison est perdue. Fyuu désire la leur rendre et vous a demandé de la reprendre des griffes des pirates. Empruntez un elbst à Pahh et récupérez trois <var 33 ((EObj)) 0DF61E94220302 /var>.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_02<tab>You have relieved the Coral Tridents on the trading vessel of their ill-gotten cargo. Return to Novv's Nursery and deliver the crates to Fyuu.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez repris les <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E898B0302 /var>. Allez les porter à Fyuu à la Couvée de Novv.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_03<tab>You have deposited the captured vessel's cargo at the feet of the young beastman. Fyuu hopes that by returning the crates in person, the shorewalkers will come to realize that not all Sahagin are creatures of violence and villainy.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez remis à Fyuu les mar<var 16 /var>chan<var 16 /var>di<var 16 /var>ses volées. Il veut les livrer en personne au capitaine du navire afin de lui prouver que tous les Sahuagins ne sont pas des pirates sans foi ni loi.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_TODO_00<tab>Reclaim cargo crates from the deck of the merchantman.
TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the cargo crates to Fyuu.
TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_000<tab>Pshhh... The piracy of the Coral Tridentsss continues unabated─they have ssstruck another trading vessel.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_000<tab>Fsshhh<var 1D /var>! Les actes de piraterie des Tridents du corail continuent de plus belle<var 1D /var>! Ils ont attaqué un autre navire marchand<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_001<tab>The merchantman's captain and crew were able to essscape in a landing ssskiff, but they were forced to abandon their shhhip─and its cargo─to their attackers.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_001<tab>L'équipage a réussi à sss'enfuir sur des canots, mais ils ont été obligés d'abandonner leurs mar<var 16 /var>chan<var 16 /var>di<var 16 /var>ses.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_002<tab>I am of a mind to sssee this cargo returned to the shhhorewalkers. Pshhh... Perhapsss it is time you practiced a little piracy of your own! Ssspeak with Pahh and borrow an elbssst─his ssseabeast will sssoon catch up to your burdened target.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_002<tab>J'aimerais qu'elles leur sssoient retournées. Fsshhh... Peut-être est-il temps pour toi de pratiquer un peu de piraterie de ton côté<var 1D /var>! Demande à Pahh de te prêter un elbssst pour te rendre sssur le bateau.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_003<tab>Take an elbssst, and make your way to the Trident-infesssted merchantman. Let us sssee what cargo you can retrieve for the shhhorewalkers.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_003<tab>Monte sur un elbssst et rejoins le navire marchand infesssté de Tridents. Empare-toi <var 33 ((EventItem)) 09F61E898B0302 /var> pour que nous puissions les rendre à leurs pro<var 16 /var>prié<var 16 /var>taires.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_TAMER01376_000_010<tab>Pshhh... The captured merchantman? My elbssst will have you sssnapping at its rudder before you've sssettled in the sssaddle.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_TAMER01376_000_010<tab>Fsshhh, le navire marchand capturé<var 1D /var>? Mon elbssst t'emmènera là-bas avant que tu aies le temps de t'asseoir cor<var 16 /var>rec<var 16 /var>te<var 16 /var>ment en ssselle<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_Q1_000_000<tab>Ride the elbst to the merchantman?
TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_020<tab>Shhhorewalker, were you able to sssteal back the cargo?
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_020<tab>Alors, sssans-branchies, as-tu pu récupérer les mar<var 16 /var>chan<var 16 /var>di<var 16 /var>ses volées<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_025<tab>Pshhh... Thank you. We will deliver these cratesss ourssselves.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_025<tab>Fsshhh, merccci. Le frai va ssse charger de les rendre au capitaine du navire.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_026<tab>The crew of the merchantman may be alarmed by our appearance, but we mussst make an effort to teach them that not all Sssahagin desire conflict and chaosss.
target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_FYUU_000_026<tab>Nous devons lui montrer que tous les Sssahuagins ne désirent pas la guerre.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_POPMESSAGE_000_000<tab>A watchful surftooth sentry attempts to prevent you from taking the crate!

target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_POPMESSAGE_000_001<tab>Action impossible. Vous devez d'abord abattre tous les ennemis.

source: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_BALLOON_000_030<tab>Pshhh! You will not have our shhhpoils!

target: TEXT_BANSAH109_01387_BALLOON_000_031<tab>Fshhh, on leur coupe la main aux voleurs<var 1D /var>!
